 Jojo|title = Sarah Geronimo is \"Pop Queen\" \u2013 Regine Velasquez|newspaper = Manila Bulletin|date = October 3, 2005|url = http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1G1-137033180.html|accessdate = January 25, 2010}}</ref> -->\n\n<!-- <ref name=\"Return Of The Champions\">{{cite news|last = Lo|first = Ricardo F.|title = The Champions did it again!|newspaper = The Philippine Star|date = June 2, 2005|url = http://www.carouselpinoy.com/rotcarticles.html|accessdate = January 25, 2010}}</ref> -->\n\n<ref name=\"Bituing Walang Ningning\">{{cite news|last = Bonoan|first = Reggee|title = Aiai, support on Sarah and Angelika|publisher = philstar.com|date = February 18, 2006|url = http://www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=322320&publicationSubCategoryId=96|accessdate = January 25, 2010}}</ref>\n\n<!-- <ref name=\"Sarah Geronimo is future of OPM\">{{cite news |last = Panaligan|first = Jojo P.|title = Famed international producer affirms Sarah Geronimo is future of OPM|newspaper = Manila Bulletin |date = July 23, 2006 |url = http://findarticles.com/p/news-articles/manila-bulletin/mi_7968/is_2006_July_23/famed-international-producer-affirms-sarah/ai_n34353817/|accessdate = March 7, 2010}}</ref> -->\n\n<!-- <ref name=\"Becoming album article\">{{cite news|last = Asilo|first = Rito|title = Sarah takes a welcome breather|publisher = Philippine Daily Inquirerr|date = December 29, 2006|url = http://showbizandstyle.inquirer.net/entertainment/entertainment/view/20061229-40810/Sarah_takes_a_welcome_breather|accessdate = January 25, 2010}}</ref> -->\n\n<ref name=\"Sarah's US tour\">{{cite news|last = de Asis|first = Raymond|title = Sarah Geronimo in US tour: Simply beyond her wildest imagination|publisher =philstar.com|date = November 19, 2006 |url = http://www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=369588&publicationSubCategoryId=70|accessdate = January 25, 2010}}</ref>\n\n<!-- <ref name=\"philstar2006\">{{cite news|title = Sarah, Returned by filipinos in US|publisher = philstar.com|date = Oc